{"tid":932635,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【布拉格諜影】捷克情報機關：5年間揭發數十名中俄間諜","createTime":"2018-12-08T02:04:40.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-08T03:14:39.000Z","uid":28765,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"804d2256f0b851b70dc0e544ab810e76d25b3ccb","tid":932635,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-08T02:04:40.000Z","msg":"捷克情報機關指出，在過去5年，發現「數十名」俄羅斯和一些中國間諜。<br />\n情報機關BIS總監考迪加(Michal Koudelka)說，這些間諜身份敗露後，有關國家已停止在捷克的間諜活動。<br />\n在多數情況下，捷克當局會拒絕承認那些嫌疑間諜的外交身份或私下要求他們離境，以免造成外交糾紛。<br />\n考迪加的言論是回應親俄和親中的捷克總統澤曼(Milos Zeman)周四對BIS的批評。BIS周一提交年報，警告俄羅斯和中國間諜對捷克和其他歐盟和北約國家的威脅，又指俄羅斯「明顯」背後策劃網絡攻擊捷克外交部。<br />\n澤曼批評情報機關超越權限及把權力「政治化」，他說，報告欠缺實質證據和中俄間諜活動的案例。不過，捷克總理巴比什(Andrej Babis)不認同澤曼的批評，表示政府對BIS的報告並無不滿。<br />\n德新社/美聯社  <br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20181208/59005741\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181208%2F59005741&d=OSJohsYyHL5iu1o8J2i1J7ZGMQxn7aheim1dKZ3ASAU%3D&h=aef7cc41\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181208%2F59005741&h=b5942dfe\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20181208/59005741</a>"},{"pid":"96ce0a729e6074f40592979de2ff6f3fe4ac3a6b","tid":932635,"uid":19527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-08T02:15:19.000Z","msg":"捷克好撚親支<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5388cca9936c132eb467027536b7d1b1afaf1ed","tid":932635,"uid":51200,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-08T02:52:04.000Z","msg":"捷克有啲料到<br />\n果然係前蘇聯國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"033e596df78d904ec441fd9c67c7a6e74c08683a","tid":932635,"uid":5